Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Voy a venirme otra vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Me vengo! Ohh... ¡Oh, me corro!
